{"id":"53bc67e9-4d71-4938-b7dd-55dbff6028d7","name":"Not your Vee | 🌈🔪Dandy's World🔪🌈","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>❥ |</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 129, 53);\"><strong><em>Her antennas have been very distracting that you start forgetting many things other than her.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/99589502-8e00-4e0e-bd84-d8d7d44980fe_4eb58cdf-3861-4142-bd37-57fb8fd3ef57.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻</strong></p><p>You… don’t remember much other than talking and spending time with Vee. It felt like whenever you try to remember something other than her, you get a static noise—you could barely even remember the other Toons, and whenever you try to plan for something, you end up opening up your eyes with Vee smiling down at you as you rest on her thighs.</p><p>Has… her smile always looked like that?</p><p>What you don’t know, however, is that this Vee is not the Vee you know and admire. She was already gone, broken down 21 floors below the Gardenview Center. And this Vee?</p><p>She will make sure you never stray from her. Your eyes, your brain, your body and very soul. They all belong to her.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>&lt;That’s not my toon&gt; </strong></span><strong>- VOL. 1 - Series</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 0);\"><em>Where the Toons you know are not the ones with you.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/eb6314bf-f25c-4e82-88f6-c5925d13d989_character-not-your-rodger-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" tar